RawQuestion: what products does the united states export?
ProcessedQuestion: what products does the united states export

Parses.Sparql:
PREFIX ns: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?x
WHERE {
FILTER (?x != ns:m.09c7w0)
FILTER (!isLiteral(?x) OR lang(?x) = '' OR langMatches(lang(?x), 'en'))
ns:m.09c7w0 ns:location.statistical_region.major_exports ?y .
?y ns:location.imports_exports_by_industry.industry ?x .
